<HEADLINE>
FT  04 MAY 91 / Appointments: Pfizer chairman
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
PFIZER, Sandwich, has appointed Mr Hugh O'Connor as chairman. He was
managing director, and succeeds Mr Ian Wilson who has retired. Mr O'Connor
joined the company as managing director a year ago. He had previously been
managing director of the Pfizer Chemical Corporation at Ringaskiddy in the
Republic of Ireland, and has been with the group for over 20 years. Mr
Wilson becomes a non-executive director.
</TEXT>
