FT  04 MAY 91 / London Stock Exchange: Dealings
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Details of business done shown below have been taken with consent from last
Thursday's Stock Exchange Official List and should not be reproduced without
permission.
Details relate to those securities not included in the FT Share Information
Services.
Unless otherwise indicated prices are in pence. The prices are those at
which the business was done in the 24 hours up to 5 pm on Thursday and
settled through the Stock Exchange Talisman system, they are not in order of
execution but in ascending order which denotes the day's highest and lowest
dealings.
For those securities in which no business was recorded in Thursday's
Official List the latest recorded business in the four previous days is
given with the relevant date.
Rule 535(2) and Third Market stocks are not regulated by the International
Stock Exchange of the United Kingdom and the Republic of Ireland Ltd.
*** Bargains at special prices. ** Bargains done the previous day.
