INVESTMENT BANK has made the following appointments: Mr Nigel L. Davies,
director, banking and treasury; Mr Kenneth E. Lillie, director, treasury
advisory, currency management and treasury systems; Mr Peter F. Pollard,
financial controller, to director; Mr Michael B. Cannan, chief executive,
