HARTSTONE GROUP: in its 1-for-1 rights issue, acceptances have been received
in respect of 28.68m new ordinary (96.4 per cent).
*****
PICT PETROLEUM has agreed to earn a 5 per cent working interest in Block 115
offshore Vietnam, subject to the approval of the Vietnamese government.
*****
REDLAND'S subsidiary Braas, through its Austrian company Bramac, has formed
a joint venture in Czechoslovakia to make concrete roof tiles. Redland
already has joint ventures in Hungary and Yugoslavia.
*****
RENTOKIL GROUP has acquired the tropical plants business of City Gardens, of
Boston, US, for an initial Dollars 10m (Pounds 6m) in cash, with further
payments up to Dollars 3m dependent on profits.
